&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Don’t See the Right Role? Let’s Talk.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We move quickly, and sometimes new opportunities take shape before they make it to our careers page! If you’re excited about building tools that help engineering teams collaborate better, tell us about your background and the kind of work you&#39;re interested in.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Our Ideal Candidate&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At CoLab, the people who make the biggest impact tend to share a few things in common:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Drive better ways of working: &lt;/strong&gt;You don’t default to “how it’s always been done.” You ask questions, challenge assumptions, and look for practical ways to improve how we operate.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Operate with ownership:&lt;/strong&gt; You take responsibility for outcomes, not just tasks. You follow through, close loops, and don’t wait to be told what to do when something needs fixing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Elevate the people around you&lt;/strong&gt;: You show respect in every interaction, give honest feedback, and contribute to a team that’s aligned and improving together.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Teams &amp;amp; Opportunities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Building a category-defining product takes talented people across many teams. We’re always interested in meeting people who want to contribute in areas such as:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Customer Success&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Development&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Finance&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Marketing&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;People&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Product&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sales&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;1077&quot; data-end=&quot;1099&quot;&gt;Note for students: &lt;/strong&gt;CoLab hires students through direct partnerships with universities and colleges, working through their co-op and internship placement programs. We’re not reviewing applications through this posting—please connect with your school’s co-op or career office for opportunities with CoLab.&lt;/

