&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Role Summary&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a senior, high-leverage operator reporting into the Director of Industry Strategy &amp;amp; Transformation, with direct exposure to revenue management and account owners. You own the strategy and execution behind CoLab&#39;s most important European enterprise deals, define how we land and expand within the region&#39;s most demanding manufacturers, build the repeatable motions that scale wins across the European revenue org, and ensure CoLab maintains product market fit as we grow in the region.&lt;/p&gt;
