&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Co-own enterprise deal strategy on CoLab&#39;s most strategic European opportunities and develop the executive-level deal plays that unblock our highest-value, most complex deals across the regional pipeline.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Run executive, management, and user workshops that surface transformation goals, expose workflow friction, and build the case for change at the pace European buying groups actually move.&lt;/li&gt;
