&lt;p&gt;In your role as Major Account Director, you will play a critical role in the growth and expansion of existing CoLab customers. You will work with current enterprise customer accounts to achieve business outcomes with industry-relevant solutions. In this role, you build and execute strategies to help land and expand 7-figure accounts. The ideal person for this role is passionate about helping others succeed and cultivating strong relationships.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
