&lt;p&gt;CoLab has major accounts with meaningful expansion potential, and a top 100 list of strategic prospects we want to win. Today, that motion is mostly account team-led. Customer success and sales own the relationship and pull in brand design or product marketing reactively. What we don’t have yet is a proactive strategy to influence new (and more senior) stakeholders, shape perceptions about our brand and product, and drive pipeline (expansion + new biz) within our Top 100 accounts. That’s where you come in.&lt;/p&gt;
