&lt;p&gt;This isn’t just a design role—it’s a leadership role within our UX design org. As a UX Designer, you’ll be an integral design contributor across our various Build Teams You’ll be responsible for many of the most technically demanding and strategically critical areas of the product.&lt;/p&gt;
