&lt;p&gt;You’re someone who enjoys doing the hard work of clarity.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You’re comfortable learning complex domains and explaining them precisely — not by simplifying them into buzzwords, but by understanding how things actually work. You can take a vague idea (“this could be a big launch”) and turn it into a concrete, executable plan with clear messaging and next steps.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You’ll thrive here if you:&lt;/p&gt;
