&lt;li&gt;See strategic guardrails as a shortcut to stakeholder alignment, not a cumbersome restriction&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ask sharp questions and respectfully push for clarity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Care deeply about whether your work actually lands with customers and internal teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Enjoy fast paced marketing with quick and frequent iterations&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You’re less likely to enjoy this role if you:&lt;/p&gt;
